 held various sales business development and leadership positions at sun microsystems and att business services elisa was recently named a woman of influence by the silicon valley business journal and has served on the board of directors for amber alert gps and rmg networks she also is an innovation advisor to the nonprofit organization equality now she serves as a judge for the annual forbes cloud  and has served as a judge for the wsj marketers that matter awards elisa was also named a top executive by social media marketing magazine in  elisa formally served on the interactive advertising bureau iab board of directors and executive committee from 0 and the forbes executive women advisory board in  advertising age named elisa a “woman to watch” she is currently a member and volunteers for national charity league donating time and resources in her local school community elisa holds a master of business administration degree from san francisco state university and a bachelor’s degree in business administration from the university of new hampshire elisa steele serves on the board of directorsposts by elisa steele august  0elisa steelethe new future of work a peek into jive’s future history jive ceo elisa steele discusses how jive is wellpositioned to continue being the foundation that makes work happen — today tomorrow and well into the future topics jive news ebook the future of intranets and enterprise social networks—why businesses need an interactive intranet the future of intranets and enterprise social networks e‑bookget the ebook february  0elisa steele years of jiving february is a big milestone for jive—we are celebrating our th birthday topics jive news january  0elisa steelethree predictions for driving modern workstyles in 0 as our world is increasingly connected people are engaging in ways that we could not have even imagined just a few decades ago who would have thought that a preteen… september  0elisa steeleworkplace flexibility what’s your workstyle 