 to add elisa steele to our leadership ranks as she possesses both the passion and experience to promote protect and grow the skype brand” “i am very excited to join the team at skype” said elisa steele “skype is known for innovation excellent product experiences and a great brand i am looking forward to working with the team and supporting the continued growth of the business globally” elisa has extensive experience leading global marketing at technology companies and joins skype after serving as evp and chief marketing officer at yahoo during her time at yahoo she was responsible for the companys global marketing strategy and functions including brand consumer businessbusiness research  insights communications policy privacy and regional marketing prior to yahoo elisa she was senior vice president of corporate marketing at netapp where she led a transformational global brand strategy for the company she was responsible for the companys new strategic positioning and the execution of marketing programs communications corporate relations and integrated marketing functions before netapp elisa led sun microsystems integrated marketing and merchandising organization where she was responsible for global gotomarket initiatives campaign execution events digital marketing and installedbase marketing her experience also includes marketing management positions at iplanet ecommerce solutions and javasoft elisa was a top performing sales leader at att for several years producing revenue growth nationally and managing diverse sales organizations elisa holds a masters of business administration degree from san francisco state university and a bachelor in business administration from the university of new hampshire about skype skype is communications software whose purpose is to break down barriers to communication with an internetconnected device families friends and colleagues can get together for free with messaging voice and video at low cost they can also call landlines or mobiles virtually anywhere in the world founded in 0 and based in luxembourg skype is a division of microsoft corp nasdaq msft skype can be downloaded onto computers mobile phones and other connected devices for free at wwwskypecom  photosmultimedia gallery available httpwwwbusinesswirecomcgibinmmgcgieid7langen contacts skypebrian o’shaughnessybrianoshskypenetorsravanthi agrawal 7  sravanthiagrawalskypenet release summary skype today announced the addition of elisa steele to its senior management team as corporate vice president of marketing elisa will oversee skype’s global brand and marketing functions contacts skypebrian o’shaughnessybrianoshskypenetorsravanthi agrawal 7  sravanthiagrawalskypenet search advanced news search advanced news search log in sign up elisa steele to participate in g women’s leadership forum skip navigation jive software is now a part oflearn more about the acquisition ×jive software is now a part of aurea × jive softwareblogjive ceo elisa steele to join panel at g women’s leadership acceleration spring  forum rss jive ceo elisa steele to join panel at g women’s leadership acceleration spring  forum june  topics jive news linkedin twitter google facebook email a critical component of leadership is making good decisions—the uncertain environment and velocity of business change create constant pressure for timely and effective decisionmaking jive ceo elisa steele will address this topic during a panel at the exclusive g women’s leadership acceleration spring  forum on thursday june  from  –  pm at the parc  hotel in san francisco elisa will be joined onstage by helen wesley cfo of enmax and maggie wilderotter the former ceo of frontier communications and panel moderator the session will dig into how to understand hidden biases that influence decisions the role of judgement when one doesn’t have all the information but needs to make a call and how to harness the power of an organization to improve the decisionmaking process elisa steele to joi